# ğŸŒ€ FleetingViews â€” View Management & Navigation for Flet

FleetingViews is a lightweight and powerful view management system for [Flet](https://flet.dev) apps.  
It helps you structure your app around clean views, guards, transitions, and reactive state â€” inspired by the best practices of modern frontend frameworks.

Think of it as a **router + state manager + lifecycle engine** for Flet.

---

## ğŸš€ Features at a Glance

âœ… Easy view registration  
âœ… Route-based navigation with history  
âœ… Lifecycle hooks (`on_mount`, `on_dismount`)  
âœ… Guards (protect views based on logic)  
âœ… Reactive observables (`define_observable`, `subscribe`)  
âœ… Two-way data binding with controls (`bind_to_control`)  
âœ… Dynamic view transitions with animations  
âœ… Built-in fallback 404 view  
âœ… Shared global state (`set_shared`, `get_shared`)  
âœ… JSON state persistence (coming soon)

